    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is strictly an 'as-is' purchase. The exterior has significant rust along the wheel wells and door bottoms, along with several noticeable dents and faded paint. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and will require immediate professional attention, and the transmission shifts harshly. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or a source for spare parts.",
